subject: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (Iran) Remission Order
precis: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (Iran) Remission Order in order to remit fees associated with travel documents, citizenship certificates and consular services that were not collected from Canadians and permanent residents of Canada in Iran from February 9, 2023 to February 28, 2025.
